---
import ContentWidth from "../components/ContentWidth.astro";
import ContactForm from "../components/ContactForm.astro";
import { Icon } from "astro-icon/components";
---

<section
        id="contact"
        class="relative py-20 bg-gradient-to-b from-black via-[#1A001D] to-black overflow-hidden"
>
    <ContentWidth>
        <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-12 items-center">
            <div class="space-y-6 text-center md:text-left motion-safe:animate-fade-in">
                <h2 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-serif text-white leading-tight drop-shadow-lg">
                    Conectemos contigo
                </h2>
                <p class="text-gray-300 text-lg leading-relaxed max-w-md mx-auto md:mx-0">
                    Déjanos un mensaje y descubre cómo nuestros zumos de uva La Vid pueden acompañar tus momentos más especiales.
                </p>

                <div class="flex flex-col gap-4 mt-8">
                    <a
                            href="mailto:contacto@lavid.life"
                            class="flex items-center justify-center md:justify-start gap-3 text-gray-300 hover:text-[#C84485] transition-colors"
                    >
                        <Icon name="mdi:email" class="w-6 h-6 text-[#C84485]" />
                        contacto@lavid.life
                    </a>
                    <a
                            href="tel:+51932508739"
                            class="flex items-center justify-center md:justify-start gap-3 text-gray-300 hover:text-[#C84485] transition-colors"
                    >
                        <Icon name="mdi:phone" class="w-6 h-6 text-[#C84485]" />
                        +51 972 252 744
                    </a>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="motion-safe:animate-slide-in-right">
                <div class="bg-black/50 backdrop-blur-md rounded-2xl shadow-lg p-8 border border-[#C84485]/40 hover:border-[#C84485]/70 transition">
                    <ContactForm />
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </ContentWidth>
</section>
